      <title>World CO₂ Emissions Growth with Dashboard using Tableau</title>
      <dc:creator>Miftahul Hadi</dc:creator>
      <link>https://miftahulhadii.github.io/posts/2022-12-20-world-co2-emissions-growth-using-tableau</link>
